{"tid":385460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台考慮今晚改發三號強風信號","createTime":"2017-09-03T08:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T04:07:39.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2dc0c9d0b1431b873a029fe57c8887b09fcb86c5","tid":385460,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1352081_1_L_20170903164109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1352081_1_L_20170903164109.jpg&h=c7446da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一號戒備信號生效。天文台說，強烈熱帶風暴瑪娃向較西北方向移動，預計今晚午夜前後在汕尾登陸並減弱，但瑪娃仍會進一步接近本港，天文台會於今晚考慮改發三號強風信號。<br />\n<br />\n天文台又表示，晚間風勢會增強，明日稍後風勢會緩和。隨着瑪娃移近香港，相關雨帶會影響珠三角一帶，明日初時會有大雨和狂風雷暴。"},{"pid":"36a476964f4ac28439ec64e391b66dbdc9beecfb","tid":385460,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:49:47.000Z","msg":"打唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54e5347cc8fadf30f6cc8600ee47ca0c50be8a4","tid":385460,"uid":54733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:51:02.000Z","msg":"標題加個日期得唔得"},{"pid":"741aa194b3347ac401a454eb395499f6ba69171d","tid":385460,"uid":70205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌，唔開心"},{"pid":"03a0d5308aa4b4b02e02c8247a623465df783e1f","tid":385460,"uid":20265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T04:07:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}